{
  "title": "Home IDS 🛡️ Tier 2: DNS & Machine Learning Diagnostics",
  "uid": "ids-tier2-dns",
  "tags": ["ids", "tier2", "dns", "ml", "showcase"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "refresh": "10s",
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      { "name": "PROMETHEUS_DS", "type": "datasource", "query": "prometheus", "label": "Prometheus Source" },
      { "name": "LOKI_DS", "type": "datasource", "query": "loki", "label": "Loki Source" },
      { "name": "device", "type": "query", "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" }, "query": "label_values(home_ids_risk_score, hostname)", "refresh": 1, "includeAll": true, "customAllValue": ".*", "multi": false, "current": { "text": "All", "value": ".*" } }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🧭 [Triage Hub](/d/ids-master-hub-ultimate?var-device=${device}) | **📊 DNS & ML Diagnostics** | [🔒 Network & Lateral (Zeek NDR)](/d/ids-tier2-ndr/home-ids-tier-2-network-lateral-zeek-ndr?var-device=${device}) | [🌍 GeoIP & OSINT Intel](/d/ids-tier2-geo/home-ids-tier-2-geoip-osint-intel?var-device=${device}) | [⚙️ Engine System Health](/d/ids-system-health/home-ids-tier-2-engine-system-health)"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🤖 Threat: ML Behavioral Anomalies & Risk Velocity\n**How to read this section:** The IsolationForest AI engine tracks how a device historically behaves and flags extreme deviations. \n* 🟢 **Normal:** ML Score stays very close to 0.00.\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** An ML Score > 0.05 means the device is acting 'out of character'. If accompanied by high Risk Velocity, the device suddenly drastically changed its behavior in the last 5 minutes. Check the Loki logs to see *which* features (like query rate or unique domains) triggered the AI."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "ML Anomaly Score (IsolationForest)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_ml_anomaly_score{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.02 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 0, "lineWidth": 2 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Max ML Score",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "max(home_ids_ml_anomaly_score{hostname=~\"$device\"})" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.05 } ] } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Risk Velocity Z-Score",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_risk_velocity{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 4 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "🔎 Filtered Workspace: ML Mathematical Outliers (Loki)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${LOKI_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "{job=\"home_ids_alerts\", environment=\"production\"} | json | device_hostname=~\"$device\" |~ \"(?i)ml anomaly|risk velocity\"" } ],
      "options": { "showLabels": false, "wrapLogMessage": true, "enableLogDetails": true }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: DGA vs Ad-Block Noise",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 21 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 🚨 Threat: Ransomware, DGA & Evasion\n**How to hunt DGA (Domain Generation Algorithms):** Malware uses DGA to randomly guess thousands of gibberish domains (e.g., `xkqztp.ru`) to find a hidden server. \n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** Look for a simultaneous vertical spike in **New Domains** AND **NXDOMAIN Ratio** (failures). If NXDOMAIN TLD Concentration is > 80%, the malware is hyper-focusing its failed guesses on a specific suffix like `.ru`.\n**How to hunt Evasion (Blocked Ratio):**\n* 🟡 **Benign:** Smart TVs hitting 80% Blocked Ratio is normal ad-blocker noise. The Z-Score will be low (between -2 and +2).\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** If Blocked Z-Score > 4.0, a device is wildly surging its attempts to bypass Pi-hole restrictions. Check the Loki logs to see *which* domain is being spammed."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "New Domains (DGA Burst Tracker)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_new_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 80 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Suspicious / Algorithmic Domains",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_suspicious_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 80 } ] }, "custom": { "drawStyle": "bars", "fillOpacity": 60 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Deep Domains (Tunneling Labels > 5)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 25 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_deep_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 80 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NXDOMAIN Ratio (Lookup Failures)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_nxdomain_ratio{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.3 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.5 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "NXDOMAIN TLD Concentration",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_nxdomain_tld_concentration{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.7 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Blocked Ratio (Absolute)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_blocked_ratio{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 0.8 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Blocked Ratio Z-Score (Evasion Spike)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 33 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "home_ids_zscore_blocked_ratio{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}}" } ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "red", "value": 4 } ] }, "custom": { "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    },
    {
      "type": "logs",
      "title": "🔎 Filtered Workspace: Ransomware, Block Evasion & DGA (Loki)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 41 },
      "datasource": { "type": "loki", "uid": "${LOKI_DS}" },
      "targets": [ { "expr": "{job=\"home_ids_alerts\", environment=\"production\"} |~ \"(?i)nxdomain ratio|blocked dns ratio|suspicious.*dga|first-seen domain burst|nxdomain tld concentration|probationary|correlated dns baseline\" | json | device_hostname=~\"$device\"" } ],
      "options": { "showLabels": false, "wrapLogMessage": true, "enableLogDetails": true }
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "📖 Analyst Field Guide: Adaptive Corridor",
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 49 },
      "transparent": true,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### 📈 Threat: Query Saturation\n**How to read this section:** The corridor chart overlays live traffic against its own established mathematical 'norm' based on the time of day.\n* 🔴 **Threat Hunt:** Solid traffic lines breaking violently through the dotted red 'Threat Limit' ceiling triggers volume alerts."
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Threat Thresholds vs Safe Baseline Corridor (Query Rate)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 52 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "home_ids_query_rate{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} - Live" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_query_rate_baseline_mean{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} - Mean" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_query_rate_threshold_limit{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} - Limit" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "custom": { "fillOpacity": 0, "lineWidth": 2 } },
        "overrides": [
          { "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*Mean.*" }, "properties": [ { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [ 10, 10 ], "fill": "dash" } }, { "id": "custom.lineWidth", "value": 1 } ] },
          { "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": ".*Limit.*" }, "properties": [ { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "dash": [ 5, 5 ], "fill": "dash" } }, { "id": "custom.fillBelowTo", "value": ".*Mean.*" }, { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 15 }, { "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } } ] }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Baseline Deviations (Z-Scores) — Behavioral Threats",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 52 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${PROMETHEUS_DS}" },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "home_ids_zscore_query_rate{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} Query-Z" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zscore_nxdomain_ratio{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} NX-Z" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zscore_suspicious_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} DGA-Z" },
        { "expr": "home_ids_zscore_unique_domains{hostname=~\"$device\"}", "legendFormat": "{{hostname}} Unique-Z" }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [ { "color": "green", "value": 0 }, { "color": "yellow", "value": 3 }, { "color": "red", "value": 6 } ] }, "custom": { "lineWidth": 2, "fillOpacity": 10 } } }
    }
  ]
}